commentTextItems.html: Gone! tossed, on off, bounces and turns away , gets the leading edge flies to lone second slip who hangs on to it.

commentPostTextItems.html: And with that Afghanistan takes the series. Zimbabwe have been outclassed and outplayed, after being rolld over for 54. Only two batsmen managed double figures. A Hamza was peak of the bowlers with 3 for 20 in 4 overs.
Man Of The Match is Rahmat Shah for his fifty.
5:40 pm That will be all from us for the series. Congratulations to Afghanistan for winning the series. Cheers all
